# deepgram.toml Requirements

## File Format
```toml
[meta]
title = "Go Voice Agent Starter" # title of the app
description = "Get started using Deepgram's Voice Agent with this Go demo app" # description of the app
author = "Deepgram DX Team <devrel@deepgram.com> (https://developers.deepgram.com)" # contact details of the DX team
useCase = "Agent" # or TTS, Agent, TextIntel,
language = "Go" # the language used in the main file
framework = "Node" # short key for the framework, or remove if null
sdk = "3.8.12" # version of the SDK, or remove if no SDK used

[build]
command = "npm install" # the command to set up the app to run it

[post-build]
message = "Run `go run main.go` to get started." # the command the user will run to start the app as a web server
```